Name: Undercover Missions: Operation Kursk K-141

You are agent Belyaeva, a secret agent hunting the criminal mastermind. After an undercover partner goes missing you must find the culprit before Kursk K-141 and the truth fall to the bottom of the ocean! Solve unique puzzles, engage with interesting characters, and hunt for clues in your search for the truth!
